<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/21236484">如何理解与评价动画短片《前进，达瓦里希》？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="675290" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">北京电影学院动画学院 2013 级毕业作品《前进，达瓦里希》<br><div class="video-box" data-swfurl="http://www.tudou.com/v/170946387/v.swf"><div class="video-box-inner">              <div class="video-thumb">                <img class="video-thumbnail" src="http://i4.tdimg.com/170/946/387/p.jpg"><i class="video-play-icon"></i>              </div>              <div class="video-box-body">                <div class="video-title">毕业创作《前进，达瓦里希》</div>                <div class="video-url">http://www.tudou.com/programs/view/m8kbq9cRXg0/?bid=03</div>              </div>            </div></div><br>本片艺术评价点击链接：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/21265698" class="internal">《前进，达瓦里希》在电影、动画的技法上水平如何？</a></div>


